<p>
Hello,
</p>

<p>
  My name is John Alison and I will be the instructor for the Experimental Particle Physics Course.
Reminder that the course will be held weekly on Wednesdays from 11:00 - 12:30 PM in Osher Room B, starting on September 10th. There will be four sessions, ending on October 1st.
</p>

<p>
Here is my plan for four weeks. 
</p>

<p>
Week 1: The Standard Model and the Higgs
</p>

<p>
Week 2: The Cannon and the Camera
</p>

<p>
Week 3: The Discovery of The Higgs Boson
</p>

<p>
Week 4: Whats next ? Discussion and field trip. 
</p>

<p>
There will be no homework is there is no required reading/work before hand.
</p>

<p>
Looking forward to getting started! 
john
</p>
